-<img src=/images/site/inverted-logo_hue298048fb3b93afb5b9c93999f030d02_2048_42x0_resize_box_2.png class=d-none id=inverted-logo alt="Inverted Logo"></nav><div class="container-fluid home" id=home><style>#homePageBackgroundImageDivStyled{background-image:url(https://jadenstittsworth.com/images/site/background3_hu3d03a01dcc18bc5be0e67db3d8d209a6_253214_500x0_resize_q75_box.jpg)}@media(min-width:500px) and (max-width:800px){#homePageBackgroundImageDivStyled{background-image:url(https://jadenstittsworth.com/images/site/background3_hu3d03a01dcc18bc5be0e67db3d8d209a6_253214_800x0_resize_q75_box.jpg)}}@media(min-width:801px) and (max-width:1200px){#homePageBackgroundImageDivStyled{background-image:url(https://jadenstittsworth.com/images/site/background3_hu3d03a01dcc18bc5be0e67db3d8d209a6_253214_1200x0_resize_q75_box.jpg)}}@media(min-width:1201px) and (max-width:1500px){#homePageBackgroundImageDivStyled{background-image:url(https://jadenstittsworth.com/images/site/background3_hu3d03a01dcc18bc5be0e67db3d8d209a6_253214_1500x0_resize_q75_box.jpg)}}@media(min-width:1501px){#homePageBackgroundImageDivStyled{background-image:url(https://jadenstittsworth.com/images/site/background3.jpg)}}</style><span class=on-the-fly-behavior></span><div id=homePageBackgroundImageDivStyled class="background container-fluid"></div><div class="container content text-center"><img src=/images/author/john_hu7f9991f5b5d471ecdfc6cff3db1a9fe6_6397_148x148_fit_box_2.png class="rounded-circle mx-auto d-block img-fluid" alt="Author Image"><h1 class=greeting>Hi, I am Jaden</h1><div class=typing-carousel><span id=ityped class=ityped></span><span class=ityped-cursor></span></div><ul id=typing-carousel-data><li>I am a FullStack SDET.</li><li>I am a manual tester.</li><li>I love servers.</li><li>I test UI, APIs, and Databases.</li><li>I love Automation Frameworks.</li></ul><a href=#about><i class="arrow bounce fa fa-chevron-down"></i></a></div></div><div class="container-fluid section-holder d-flex bg-white"><div class="container anchor p-lg-5 about-section" id=about><div class="row pt-sm-2 pt-md-4 align-self-center"><div class=col-sm-6><h3 class=p-1>Jaden Stittsworth</h3><h5 class=p-1>Software Developement Engineer in Test</h5><p class="p-1 text-justify">I am a passionate SDET looking for my first team. My main Language is Java. I&rsquo;ve designed and developed many DD, BD, Hybrid Framework automation test scripts for Front End and Backend projects. I am experienced with Waterfall, Agile, and Agile scrum methodologies. Teamwork and Communication are my top priorities. I&rsquo;m incredibly excited to share my knowledge and expierience. Aswell as, learn from others in order to solve new and exciting problems. I have an aptitude for learning and adapting to new projects and teams. I&rsquo;m a hard worker with a very positive outlook and a great personality!</p><div class="text-container ml-auto"><ul class="social-link d-flex"><li><a href=mailto:admin@jadenstittsworth-resume.com target=_blank><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i></a></li><li><a href=https://www.github.com/Stitts5401 target=_blank><i class="fab fa-github"></i></a></li><li><a href=# target=_blank><i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i></a></li></ul></div><a href=/files/resume.pdf target=#><button class="btn btn-dark">My resume</button></a></div><div class="col-sm-6 pt-5 pl-md-4 pl-sm-3 pt-sm-0"><div class=row><div class="col-6 col-lg-4 p-2"><div class="circular-progress blue"><span class=circular-progress-left><span class="circular-progress-bar circular-progress-percentage-85"></span></span><span class=circular-progress-right><span class=circular-progress-bar></span></span><div class=circular-progress-value>Leadership</div></div></div><div class="col-6 col-lg-4 p-2"><div class="circular-progress yellow"><span class=circular-progress-left><span class="circular-progress-bar circular-progress-percentage-100"></span></span><span class=circular-progress-right><span class=circular-progress-bar></span></span><div class=circular-progress-value>Team Work</div></div></div><div class="col-6 col-lg-4 p-2"><div class="circular-progress pink"><span class=circular-progress-left><span class="circular-progress-bar circular-progress-percentage-100"></span></span><span class=circular-progress-right><span class=circular-progress-bar></span></span><div class=circular-progress-value>Communication</div></div></div><div class="col-6 col-lg-4 p-2"><div class="circular-progress green"><span class=circular-progress-left><span class="circular-progress-bar circular-progress-percentage-100"></span></span><span class=circular-progress-right><span class=circular-progress-bar></span></span><div class=circular-progress-value>Hard Working</div></div></div><div class="col-6 col-lg-4 p-2"><div class="circular-progress sky"><span class=circular-progress-left><span class="circular-progress-bar circular-progress-percentage-90"></span></span><span class=circular-progress-right><span class=circular-progress-bar></span></span><div class=circular-progress-value>Fast Learner</div></div></div><div class="col-6 col-lg-4 p-2"><div class="circular-progress orange"><span class=circular-progress-left><span class="circular-progress-bar circular-progress-percentage-95"></span></span><span class=circular-progress-right><span class=circular-progress-bar></span></span><div class=circular-progress-value>Problem Solving</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="container-fluid section-holder d-flex bg-dimmed"><div class="container-fluid anchor pb-5 skills-section" id=skills><h1 class=text-center>Skills</h1><div class="container d-flex-block"><div class=row id=primary-skills><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-lg-4 pt-2"><a class=skill-card-link href=https://www.java.com/en/ target=_blank><div class=card><div class="card-head d-flex"><img class=card-img-xs src=/images/sections/skills/java.png alt=Java><h5 class=card-title>Java</h5></div><div class=card-body><p class=card-text>Know high-level Java programming. Follow all best practices for clean and concise code. I&rsquo;ve used this for problem solving as well as writing many Automation testing Frameworks. As well as, many handy utility packages.</p></div></div></a></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-lg-4 pt-2"><a class=skill-card-link href=https://www.mysql.com/ target=_blank><div class=card><div class="card-head d-flex"><img class=card-img-xs src=/images/sections/skills/sql.png alt=SQL><h5 class=card-title>SQL</h5></div><div class=card-body><p class=card-text>Know all Fundamentals of writing and creating queries from a database. As well as, writing automation scripts using JDBC Libraries.</p></div></div></a></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-lg-4 pt-2"><a class=skill-card-link href=https://cucumber.io/ target=_blank><div class=card><div class="card-head d-flex"><img class=card-img-xs src=/images/sections/skills/cucumber.png alt="Cucumber / Gherkin"><h5 class=card-title>Cucumber / Gherkin</h5></div><div class=card-body><p class=card-text>Extensive practice writing features, runners, step definition and User-Stories for cucumber based projects.</p></div></div></a></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-lg-4 pt-2"><a class=skill-card-link href=https://www.selenium.dev/ target=_blank><div class=card><div class="card-head d-flex"><img class=card-img-xs src=/images/sections/skills/selenium-icon.png alt="Selenium WebDriver"><h5 class=card-title>Selenium WebDriver</h5></div><div class=card-body><p class=card-text>Using Selenium Webdriver with Cucumber-JUnit for UI testing in my frameworks. Experience with parallel testing using Selenium Grid. Use things like appium for mobile testing.</p></div></div></a></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-lg-4 pt-2"><a class=skill-card-link href=https://www.atlassian.com/software/jira target=_blank><div class=card><div class="card-head d-flex"><img class=card-img-xs src=/images/sections/skills/jira.png alt=Jira><h5 class=card-title>Jira</h5></div><div class=card-body><p class=card-text>Experienced using Jira tools to write detailed User-Stories and track / report bugs.</p></div></div></a></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-lg-4 pt-2"><a class=skill-card-link href=https://www.postman.com/ target=_blank><div class=card><div class="card-head d-flex"><img class=card-img-xs src=/images/sections/skills/postman.png alt=PostMan><h5 class=card-title>PostMan</h5></div><div class=card-body><p class=card-text>I&rsquo;ve used postman&rsquo;s collection frameworks to write API test suites prior to deserialization and serialization tests within my Java Framework using REST Assured Libraries.</p></div></div></a></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-lg-4 pt-2"><a class=skill-card-link href=https://spring.io/ target=_blank><div class=card><div class="card-head d-flex"><img class=card-img-xs src=/images/sections/skills/spring_boot-icon.png alt="Spring Boot"><h5 class=card-title>Spring Boot</h5></div><div class=card-body><p class=card-text>Capable of writing Rest Controllers and working within Spring Frameworks.</p></div></div></a></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-lg-4 pt-2"><a class=skill-card-link href=http://appium.io/ target=_blank><div class=card><div class="card-head d-flex"><img class=card-img-xs src=/images/sections/skills/appium-icon.png alt=Appium><h5 class=card-title>Appium</h5></div><div class=card-body><p class=card-text>Write most of the programs as dockerized container. Experienced with multi-stage, multi-arch build process.</p></div></div></a></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-lg-4 pt-2"><a class=skill-card-link href=https://www.jenkins.io/ target=_blank><div class=card><div class="card-head d-flex"><img class=card-img-xs src=/images/sections/skills/jenkins-icon.png alt=CI/CD><h5 class=card-title>CI/CD</h5></div><div class=card-body><p class=card-text>Created Jenkins Jobs to have test suite such as: Regression and Smoke run automatically at specific time&rsquo;s and whenever developers push codes to specific branch. Allowing to fully automate deployment if tests checkout.</p></div></div></a></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-lg-4 pt-2"><a class=skill-card-link href=https://aws.amazon.com/ target=_blank><div class=card><div class="card-head d-flex"><img class=card-img-xs src=/images/sections/skills/cloud.png alt="Cloud Computing"><h5 class=card-title>Cloud Computing</h5></div><div class=card-body><p class=card-text>Worked with most of the major clouds such as GCP, AWS, Azure etc.</p></div></div></a></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-lg-4 pt-2"><a class=skill-card-link href=https://aws.amazon.com/ target=_blank><div class=card><div class="card-head d-flex"><img class=card-img-xs src=/images/sections/skills/karate.png alt="Katare DSL"><h5 class=card-title>Katare DSL</h5></div><div class=card-body><p class=card-text>Using for API automation testing, Performance, and Load testing.</p></div></div></a></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-lg-4 pt-2"><a class=skill-card-link href=javascript:void(0)><div class=card><div class="card-head d-flex"><img class=card-img-xs src=/images/sections/skills/linux.png alt=Linux><h5 class=card-title>Linux</h5></div><div class=card-body><p class=card-text>Using as the main operating system. Capable of basic navigation and editing text with VIM, sublime, atom, and more.</p></div></div></a></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-lg-4 pt-2"><a class=skill-card-link href=https://git-scm.com/ target=_blank><div class=card><div class="card-head d-flex"><img class=card-img-xs src=/images/sections/skills/git.png alt=Git><h5 class=card-title>Git</h5></div><div class=card-body><p class=card-text>Experienced with Git-based development. Mostly, use Github. Also, have experience in working with GitLab.</p></div></div></a></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-lg-4 pt-2"><a class=skill-card-link href=https://www.office.com/ target=_blank><div class=card><div class="card-head d-flex"><img class=card-img-xs src=/images/sections/skills/microsoft.png alt="Microsoft 365"><