-<span class="badge btn-info">Professionalism</span></div><div class=project-btn-holder><a class="github-button-inactive project-btn" href=https://github.com/Stitts5401/stitts5401.github.io data-icon=octicon-standard data-show-count=true aria-label="Star Personal Resume Website">Star</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="container-fluid section-holder d-flex bg-white"><div class="container-fluid anchor pb-5 accomplishments-section" id=accomplishments><h1 class=text-center>Studying</h1><div class=container><div class=row id=acomplishment-card-holder><div class="col-md-12 col-lg-6 p-2"><div class="card mt-3"><div class=card-header><h5 class="card-title mb-0">Machine Learning</h5><div class=sub-title><span><a href=https://www.coursera.org target=_blank>Coursera</a></span>
-<span class=ml-2>Jun 2020 - Jan 2021</span></div></div><div class=card-body><p>This course provides a broad introduction to machine learning, datamining, and statistical pattern recognition. Topics include: (i) Supervised learning (parametric/non-parametric algorithms, support vector machines, kernels, neural networks). (ii) Unsupervised learning (clustering, dimensionality reduction, recommender systems, deep learning). (iii) Best practices in machine learning (bias/variance theory; innovation process in machine learning and AI).</p></div><div class=card-footer></div></div></div><div class="col-md-12 col-lg-6 p-2"><div class="card mt-3"><div class=card-header><h5 class="card-title mb-0">Python</h5><div class=sub-title><span><a href=https://www.manning.com/books/the-quick-python-book-third-edition target=_blank>The Quick Python Book</a></span>
-<span class=ml-2>Jan 2021 - present</span></div></div><div class=card-body><p>This course is a complete guide to master the SDIs. It is created by hiring managers who’ve been working at Google, Facebook, Microsoft, and Amazon. We&rsquo;ve carefully chosen a set of questions that have not only been repeatedly asked at top companies, but also provide a thorough experience to handle any system design problem.</p></div><div class=card-footer></div></div></div><div class="col-md-12 col-lg-6 p-2"><div class="card mt-3"><div class=card-header><h5 class="card-title mb-0">The Apache Hadoop software library</h5><div class=sub-title><span><a href=https://www.udemy.com/course/the-ultimate-hands-on-hadoop-tame-your-big-data/ target=_blank>Udemy</a></span>
-<span class=ml-2>Jan 2021 - preset</span></div></div><div class=card-body><p>The world of Hadoop and &ldquo;Big Data&rdquo; can be intimidating - hundreds of different technologies with cryptic names form the Hadoop ecosystem. With this Hadoop tutorial, you&rsquo;ll not only understand what those systems are and how they fit together - but you&rsquo;ll go hands-on and learn how to use them to solve real business problems! Learn and master the most popular big data technologies in this comprehensive course, taught by a former engineer and senior manager from Amazon and IMDb. We&rsquo;ll go way beyond Hadoop itself, and dive into all sorts of distributed systems you may need to integrate with.</p></div><div class=card-footer></div></div></div><div class="col-md-12 col-lg-6 p-2"><div class="card mt-3"><div class=card-header><h5 class="card-title mb-0">Introduction to AI, Machine Learning and Python basics</h5><div class=sub-title><span><a href="https://www.udemy.com/course/introduction-to-ai-machine-learning-and-python-basics/?utm_source=adwords&utm_medium=udemyads&utm_campaign=MachineLearning_v.PROF_la.EN_cc.US_ti.6594&utm_content=deal4584&utm_term=_._ag_79286111246_._ad_436603255192_._kw__._de_c_._dm__._pl__._ti_dsa-774930044809_._li_9005886_._pd__._&matchtype=b&gclid=CjwKCAjw07qDBhBxEiwA6pPbHiMpmmW1ffThVAqMZSPmvSwW0cJOyxoVV6YzNVkIrbTWrjJpDKYU2xoCYq0QAvD_BwE" target=_blank>Udemy</a></span>
-<span class=ml-2>Jun 2020 - Jan 2021</span></div></div><div class=card-body><p>Artificial Intelligence has already become an indispensable part of our everyday life, whether when we browse the Internet, shop online, watch videos and images on social networks, and even when we drive a car or use our smartphones. AI is widely used in medicine, sales forecasting, space industry and construction. Since we are surrounded by AI technologies everywhere, we need to understand how these technologies work. And for such understanding at a basic level, it is not necessary to have a technical or IT education.</p></div><div class=card-footer></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="container-fluid section-holder d-flex bg-dimmed"><div class="container-fluid anchor pb-5 achievements-section" id=achievements><div class=container><div class=row id=gallery></div></div><div class=d-none id=achievements-holder><div class="achievement-entry text-center" style=background-image:url(https://jadenstittsworth.com/images/sections/achievements/pittsburgh_hua14ef57eb5e9ee153a0d369e50bb95df_19947_0x300_resize_q75_box.jpg)><i class="fas fa-search-plus" id=enlarge-icon></i><h4 class=title id=achievement-title>Home</h4><div class="caption hidden col-lg-6 text-left" id=caption><h4>Home</h4><p>Born and raised in my beautiful hometown of Pittsburgh.</p></div><span style=background-image:url(https://jadenstittsworth.com/images/sections/achievements/pittsburgh_hua14ef57eb5e9ee153a0d369e50bb95df_19947_0x300_resize_q75_box.jpg) class=d-none id=SmallImage active=true></span><span style=background-image:url(https://jadenstittsworth.com/images/sections/achievements/pittsburgh_hua14ef57eb5e9ee153a0d369e50bb95df_19947_0x1500_resize_q75_box.jpg) class=d-none id=LargeImage></span></div><div class="achievement-entry text-center" style=background-image:url(https://jadenstittsworth.com)><i class="fas fa-search-plus" id=enlarge-icon></i><h4 class=title id=achievement-title>Second Child</h4><div class="caption hidden col-lg-6 text-left" id=caption><h4>Second Child</h4><p>Worked incredibly hard throughout highschool to save up for my first dream car. Love doing all the maintenance and learning about the engine and all the parts. Would love to mod it someday.</p></div><span style=background-image:url(https://jadenstittsworth.com) class=d-none id=SmallImage active=true></span><span style=background-image:url(https://jadenstittsworth.com) class=d-none id=LargeImage></span></div><div class="achievement-entry text-center" style=background-image:url(https://jadenstittsworth.com/images/sections/achievements/league_hu48cc22606bc2e4c048328c569d24f3e9_492369_0x300_resize_box_2.png)><i class="fas fa-search-plus" id=enlarge-icon></i><h4 class=title id=achievement-title>Hobbies</h4><div class="caption hidden col-lg-6 text-left" id=caption><h4>Hobbies</h4><p>Pretty my much my main hobby besides work, my car, and helping my friends build computers. In the course of my league career I grew Duck Dynasty tier beared climbing to the top .01% of players, mastering my team skills, coordination, and communication.</p></div><span style=background-image:url(https://jadenstittsworth.com/images/sections/achievements/league_hu48cc22606bc2e4c048328c569d24f3e9_492369_0x300_resize_box_2.png) class=d-none id=SmallImage active=true></span><span style=background-image:url(https://jadenstittsworth.com/images/sections/achievements/league_hu48cc22606bc2e4c048328c569d24f3e9_492369_0x1500_resize_box_2.png) class=d-none id=LargeImage></span></div><div class="achievement-entry text-center" style=background-image:url(https://jadenstittsworth.com/images/sections/achievements/rascal_hu81607df412d401e99b1295a7403b90e6_199317_0x300_resize_q75_box.jpeg)><i class="fas fa-search-plus" id=enlarge-icon></i><h4 class=title id=achievement-title>First Child</h4><div class="caption hidden col-lg-6 text-left" id=caption><h4>First Child</h4><p>My little buddy keeps me sain while I study all day. At this point she could 